title: build: reverse buildlet failed to clean up removed file in $GOROOT?
body:
After https://golang.org/cl/9461 is submitted, the new darwin/amd64 builder
starts to fail with multiple declaration erros, which doesn't make sense, as one
of the conflicting file is removed by that CL.

http://build.golang.org/log/fd15555a76804eb108e9458bbc253a7b6ebba7b3
